      "content": "wait i'm confused lol you just said i can stop but then you said to finish the course. my doctor just gave me the prescription and didn't really explain why i have to take them for all 10 days if the infection is already gone. if i can see that the skin is totally clear, does that not mean the bacteria are dead? i'd rather just stop now so i don't get an upset stomach from the pills.",
